摘要： 必需 | 可选 详细信息： 元素

darks.orm.annotation
注释类型 OneToOne

@Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface OneToOne

Indicates the One to one relation mapping model

OneToOne.java

For example:

If you use the "semi-automatic" form, the need to manually write SQL statements 

 @OneToOne(resultType = Depart.class, SQL = "select * from t_depart where depart_id = ?")
 public Depart getUserDepart() {
      return userDepart;
 }
If you use the "automation" form, only need to specify the target class key attribute 
 @OneToOne(resultType = Depart.class, mappedBy = "departId", mappedType = MappedType.EntityType)
 public Depart getUserDepart() {
      return userDepart;
 }

从以下版本开始：
JDK1.5
版本：
1.0.0 v05/01/2012
作者：
Liu LiHua
另请参见：
OneToMany, ManyToOne

必需元素摘要
 java.lang.Class<?> resultType
          The method returns the class type
 
可选元素摘要
 java.lang.String mappedBy
          If you use the "automation" form, need to set the mappedBy to the primary key attribute of target class.
 MappedType mappedType
          Relation mapping types.
 java.lang.String SQL
          If you use the "semi-automatic" form, need to write SQL query statement.
 

元素详细信息

resultType

public abstract java.lang.Class<?> resultType
The method returns the class type

mappedBy

public abstract java.lang.String mappedBy
If you use the "automation" form, need to set the mappedBy to the primary key attribute of target class. If not, does not need the assignment.

默认值：
""

SQL

public abstract java.lang.String SQL
If you use the "semi-automatic" form, need to write SQL query statement. If not, does not need the assignment.

默认值：
""

mappedType

public abstract MappedType mappedType
Relation mapping types. "automation" or "semi-automatic"

另请参见：
MappedType
默认值：
darks.orm.annotation.MappedType.SqlType
